title: Dinwi jwng gwdan gwthar sanao
lyrics:
Dinwi jwng gwdan gwthar sanao
Fwibai jwng gwdan gwswkhou gothainw -2
(A)
Sofwinw habai jwng beao gaswi
Bekhainw Iswarkhou hambai hwnswi
Laya jwng, laya jwng -2
Khwmsini btrakhou swlwnga jwng
(B)
Jisu Krishtoni gaham btra
Swlwngwn jwng boibw rongja-baja
Laya jwng, laya jwng -2
Khwmsini btrakhou swlwnga jwng
